https://bugs.gentoo.org/929253
This worked oggz_packet embedded ogg_packet as first member, so oggz_packet->whatever and ogg_packet->whatever
were equivalent before modern C. Fix is both trivial and increases correctness if oggz decides to move
it's insides for some reason
